<plot>Sanjay (Uday Chopra) and Anjali (Tulip Joshi) are childhood chums . When Sanjay's roommate Ria (Bipasha Basu) questions him whether he has fallen for Anjali he vehemently denies . But the truth that he indeed loves her hits him like a ton of bricks when Sanjana calls him to tell that she is getting married to Rohit (Jimmy Shergill) . Sanjay wants to win Anjali's heart at any cost and sets off on his "noble" cause of stopping the marriage .</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?366381</url></doc>
